1	//! Direct expansion checks (AST-level). Each fixture mirrors a `[Qn]` oracle
2	//! observation and, for the byte-parity set, the hand-inlined `.spthy` in
3	//! ../fixtures/ that workspace/byteparity.sh proves equal to the macro theory.
